headline: Fortinet to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Financial Results
summary: SUNNYVALE, Calif., Jan. 05, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- News Summary Fortinet® (NASDAQ: FTNT), the global cybersecurity leader driving the convergence of networking and security, announced that it will hold a conference call to discuss its fourth quarter and full year 2025 financial results on Thursday, February 5, at 1:30 p.m. Pacific Time (4:30 p.m. Eastern Time). Fortinet's financial results conference call will be broadcast live in listen-only mode on the company’s investor relations website at
